! Changelog

|!Version |!Date |!Changes |
|v0.1.13 |2026-04-15 |Fix typeahead-select in field-editor: pass `sync-tiddler`/`sync-field` bindings so selections are actually written to the target field (previously silently no-op in typeahead mode) |
|v0.1.12 |2026-04-14 |New typeahead-select component for object-ref fields: search input with filtered dropdown (searches title/caption/subtitle/abbrev), selected values as compact tags with × remove. Configurable via `$:/config/rimir/typed/ref-editor` (typeahead or pills); enum fields always use pills. Typeahead is the new default |
|v0.1.11 |2026-04-13 |Fix type-chain import order so subtypes can override `rrt.fields:0()` (parent imported first, subtype last); field bar now starts with the type icon and shows `type-key: caption` on hover |
|v0.1.10 |2026-04-10 |Fix enum import: include child enum tiddler in `$importvariables` so inherited enum options resolve correctly |
|v0.1.9 |2026-04-09 |Configurable reference pill display: show title, caption, subtitle, or abbrev (settings page); applies to editor, field bar, inline field bar, and filter panel |
|v0.1.8 |2026-04-09 |Field editor: support `datetime` typed fields with time picker (showTime, 24h format) |
|v0.1.7 |2026-04-08 |Add rrt-filter unit tests (18 specs) |
|v0.1.6 |2026-04-01 |Add `nest:N` constraint for same-type nesting depth limits; filter nested items from parent pills; validator reports nesting violations |
|v0.1.5 |2026-03-23 |Add filter-panel, filter-summary, field-bar-inline components and filter styles |
|v0.1.4 |2026-03-15 |Replace inline style attributes with CSS classes, add styles.tid stylesheet |
|v0.1.3 |2026-03-15 |Add name field to plugin.info |
|v0.1.2 |2026-03-15 |Add regression tests and CI test gate |
|v0.1.1 |2026-03-06 |Standardize plugin tabs, replace license.tid with LICENSE.md.meta sidecar, rename Validator/Spawner to lowercase |
|v0.1.0 |2026 |Initial release |
